<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Micor issues further cautionary.</title>
<headline>Micor issues further cautionary.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Micor Industrial Corp Ltd said on Thursday it was still in talks which could affect the company's share price.</p>
<p>The company urged shareholders to exercise caution in their share dealings. It gave no further details in a brief statement.</p>
<p>It first cautioned shareholders on February 10.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27-11 482-1003</p>
